About ExcelAnalyze

ExcelAnalyze is a powerful and intuitive platform designed to transform the way you interact with Excel data. It empowers users to seamlessly upload, parse, and analyze spreadsheet data with cutting-edge visualization and AI-powered insights.

Why Choose ExcelAnalyze?

  • Fast & Secure Uploads: Upload your Excel files safely using our robust backend secured with JWT authorization.
  • Advanced Parsing: Utilizes powerful SheetJS to accurately parse complex spreadsheets.
  • Interactive Visualization: Create insightful 2D charts with Chart.js and stunning 3D visualizations with Three.js.
  • Downloadable Reports: Export your charts as high-quality PNG images or PDF documents for presentations and reporting.
  • History & Analytics: Maintain a detailed history of your uploads and analyses, enabling efficient record keeping and review.
  • Admin Management: Dedicated admin dashboard for managing users and monitoring platform usage.
  • Cutting-Edge AI Insights: Optionally integrate with OpenAI to generate automated insights and recommendations from your data.

Our Mission

We aim to democratize data analysis by providing accessible, effective, and intelligent tools that empower individuals and businesses to unlock the true potential of their Excel datasets.

Technology Stack

Built with a modern MERN stack:

  • MongoDB: Flexible NoSQL database to store users, files, and analyses.
  • Express.js & Node.js: Secure and scalable REST API backend.
  • React: Fast, reactive, and component-driven frontend interface.
  • Redux Toolkit: Robust state management across the app.
  • Tailwind CSS: Modern and responsive styling framework.
  • SheetJS: For efficient Excel file parsing.
  • Chart.js & Three.js: Visual data storytelling with 2D and 3D charts.
  • OpenAI API (optional): AI-assisted data insights and analysis suggestions.

And many more open-source tools and libraries...
